g.title: /contest/2
g.text: Have you received a written eviction notice?

g.title: /contest/3
g.text: Was it on the proper form?

g.title: /contest/5
g.text: Has your landlord tried to change your locks, threaten you, or harass you in any way?

g.title: /contest/6
g.text: Your notice is likely not lawful. Take some time to learn about your rights.

g.title: /contest/30
g.text: What was the reason for your eviction?

g.title: /contest/5->/contest/fletter/evc_protect
g.text: No, but I think my landlord wants to evict me

g.title: /contest/5->/contest/fletter/arb
g.text: Yes, I need to speak with an advocate right away!

g.title: /contest/6->/contest/fletter/evc_arb_technical_form
g.text: Next Step: Write a Letter to Your Landlord

g.title: /contest/7
g.text: Have more than 5 days passed since you received your eviction notice?

g.title: /contest/34
g.text: It seems like you probably missed the window to contest your eviction.

g.title: /contest/38
g.text: Are you able to pay your rent in full within 5 days of receiving this notice?

g.title: /contest/8
g.text: Have more than 10 days passed since you received notice?

g.title: /contest/35
g.text: Did your landlord indicate what specifically you did wrong?

g.title: /contest/9
g.text: Have more than 15 days passed since you received notice?

g.title: /contest/44
g.text: Do you have evidence that the reason your landlord gave for your eviction is misleading or untrue?

g.title: /contest/29
g.text: Is your living situation covered by the Residential Tenancy Act?

g.title: /contest/43
g.text: If you are not covered by the RTA you will find it hard (but not impossible) to fight back.

g.title: /contest/31
g.text: Were you given 10 Days Notice to Move Out?

g.title: /contest/30->/contest/31
g.text: I did not pay my rent or utilities in full and on time

g.title: /contest/30->/contest/32
g.text: The eviction is related to something I am alleged to have done (i.e issues with noise, guests, etc)

g.title: /contest/30->/contest/33
g.text: I am being evicted for 'no fault'

g.title: /contest/34->/contest/fletter/../landing
g.text: Please take some time to report your landlord and sign a petition to help improve the law in B.C

g.title: /contest/36
g.text: Did your landlord give you a chance to address the issue?

g.title: /contest/37
g.text: Did your landlord ever give you a formal warning?

g.title: /contest/39
g.text: Do you have evidence to counter your landlord's allegations?

g.title: /contest/38->/contest/fletter/../landing
g.text: Yes, I should pay my landlord immediately

g.title: /contest/39->/contest/fletter/evc_arb_substantive_cause_yesissue_no_warning
g.text: Yes, I have a witness or evidence to support my version of events
